   CAPTION: Baggage policy that applies to scuba diving and snorkelling
   equipment.

   Quantity Per passenger: 1 empty O^2 tank, 1 tank harness, 1 pressure
   gauge, 1 mask, 1 regulator, 1 pair of fins, 1 wet or dry suit, 1 pair
   aqua shoes/booties, 1 buoyancy compensator, 1 snorkel
