   equipment allowance (size/piece/weight) is exceeded. See details under
   Checked baggage.
   Details

   Pole tips must be covered.

   Place your skis or snowboard and poles in a ski or snowboard bag and
   your boots in a separate bag.

   CAPTION: Baggage policy that applies to surfboard/Paddleboard.

   Quantity 1 item per passenger. We strongly recommend that passengers
   arrive early as baggage hold space is limited, and the board could be
   refused for operational reasons.
