   CAD $100* per item, per flight segment

   *USD: $100 / EUR: €80 / GBP: £65
   Excess baggage charges Flat rate – see Cost (above)
   Details

   Please arrive early to allow sufficient time for proper
   handling. Additional baggage and/or excess weight is subject to space
   availability and may be refused for operational reasons.

   For more information on individual baggage items exceeding 32 kg
   (70 lb) in weight, contact our Cargo department.


   Quantity 1 mast and 1 sail (packed together but separately from the
