   CAPTION: Baggage policy that applies to electronic cigarette and
   nicotine inhaler.

   Details Electronic cigarettes are allowed provided they remain stowed
   and unused in your carry-on baggage. Carriage in checked baggage is
   prohibited. Specific country restrictions may also apply.

