   Infants travelling on an adult's lap do not have a baggage allowance;
   however, 1 stroller and 1 car seat per child/infant are accepted free
   of charge. No substitutions permitted. Additional items (such as a
   playpen, booster seat, additional car seat, etc.) exceeding your free
   checked baggage allowance (weight, size and/or number of pieces
   permitted) will be subject to excess baggage charges. Parent/guardian
   may carry diaper bag in addition to regular carry-on, containing
   supplies needed for duration of flight.
