   transfer of sporting equipment to hotels at some destinations. Please
   ensure that equipment is properly wrapped/secured for transport to
   prevent loss or damage.

   Please note that hockey equipment is considered part of a passenger’s
   baggage allowance and subject to regular baggage fees. One bag and a
   maximum of two sticks taped together count as one piece of baggage
   towards the maximum number of checked bags allowed by the fare type.

   We recommend passengers purchase additional insurance.
